perl-Gtk2-Notify
------------------------------------------
Perl bindings for libnotify (desktop notification library)

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-15
  gdk-pixbuf2-2.12.12-1
  glib2-2.16.6-1
  gtk2-x11-2.12.12-1
  libnotify-0.4.4-1
  perl-5.10.0-5
  perl-Glib-1.183-1
  perl-Gtk2-1.183-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-20080624-2
  cygport-0.4.2-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1
  perl-ExtUtils-Depends-0.301-1
  perl-ExtUtils-PkgConfig-1.11-1

Canonical website:
  http://search.cpan.org/dist/Gtk2-Notify/

Canonical download:
  http://search.cpan.org/CPAN/authors/id/F/FL/FLORA/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack perl-Gtk2-Notify-0.05-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./perl-Gtk2-Notify-0.05-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/perl-Gtk2-Notify-0.05-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/perl-Gtk2-Notify-0.05-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/Gtk2/Notify.pm
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/Gtk2/Notify.pod
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/Gtk2/Notify/Install/notify-autogen.h
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/Gtk2/Notify/Install/notify.typemap
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/Gtk2/Notify/index.pod
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/auto/Gtk2/Notify/.packlist
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/auto/Gtk2/Notify/Notify.dll
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Gtk2-Notify-0.05/Changes
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Gtk2-Notify-0.05/README
  /usr/share/man/man3/Gtk2.Notify.3pm.gz
  /usr/share/man/man3/Gtk2.Notify.index.3pm.gz

